des:
The B-105 skill gives Alexa the ability to start the B-105 online stream. WUBE-FM in Cincinnati, Ohio, features the B-105 Music Marathon, today’s best mainstream artists, exciting contests, fun promotions and the most recognized on-air personalities in country radio, including CMA and ACM Large Market Personality of the Year winners, The Big Dave Show! Listen on your Echo with the B-105 skill!
